{"tid":2437214,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"請問可以幫幫我嗎","createTime":"2021-03-07T17:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T17:43:31.000Z","uid":353433,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4658af0bd3a2626835e8c20e9a460a559bee15a4","tid":2437214,"uid":353433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"大家晚上好<br />\n<br />\n今日聽到媽咪同親戚講Daddy被測試到有輕微抑鬱症<br />\n<br />\n我聽到之後好擔心 成個人都好不知所措<br />\n<br />\n上網睇咗好多好多相關資料<br />\n<br />\n都不外乎 多關心 多聆聽 多陪伴<br />\n<br />\n請問有無朋友仔身邊都有抑鬱症的人<br />\n<br />\n請問你平時係點同佢哋相處 點樣可以幫助到佢地呢<br />\n<br />\n好希望聽下你的經驗 令我都可以幫助到爸爸<br />\n<br />\n真的感謝你的時間 亦都感謝你的分享"},{"pid":"729b5bef31eba7ab9c220bc99062833a5d59db2f","tid":2437214,"uid":22902,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T17:31:49.000Z","msg":"多聆聽佢講嘢，唔洗畀意見架聽就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多d留意佢情緒，例如見到佢刻意避開某d人同事<br />\n你可以問返佢係咪有咩令佢唔舒服<br />\n唔洗逼佢開心或者參與某d活動，佢想就陪佢<br />\n另外特別推薦玩下顏色例如和諧粉彩個d<br />\n藝術真係好幫到好多情緒病人舒發情緒<br />\n當然前提係佢都希望參與先<br />\n<br />\n我自己都係過來人，分享下少少經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c1c4782f44f1a0a1f22066380f1da2a1ca92aa","tid":2437214,"uid":344609,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T17:34:25.000Z","msg":"晚上好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CE_mxIPgRHg/?igshid=5ubd0nebelp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCE_mxIPgRHg%2F%3Figshid%3D5ubd0nebelp4&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058nGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=50d9cf9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCE_mxIPgRHg%2F%3Figshid%3D5ubd0nebelp4&h=d82df1b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CE_mxIPgRHg/?igshid=5ubd0nebelp4</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個page幫到你<br />\n<br />\n祝你同屋企人平安無事<br />\n<br />\n陪多啲佢哋 <br />\n<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"e2fdbff3b9a0d3d8df712bed7